## Summary of All Features

| Category | Feature Count | Details |
|---|---|---|
| **Renderers** | 7 | Video, Web, Metal Shader, Particles, Slideshow, Quartz Composer, Generative Art |
| **Display** | 4 | Multi-monitor, per-display control, span mode, auto-resize on display changes |
| **Performance** | 8 | FPS control (5 presets), battery detection, fullscreen app pause, CPU/memory monitoring, sleep/wake handling, space change handling |
| **Audio** | 5 | FFT analysis, bass/mid/treble split, 64-band spectrum, smoothing, forwarding to all renderers |
| **Playlist** | 6 | Auto-advance, shuffle, configurable intervals, directory scanning, add/remove/clear, previous/next |
| **Scheduling** | 3 | Day/night wallpapers, configurable sunrise/sunset hours |
| **Transitions** | 6 | None, Crossfade, Dissolve, Slide L/R, Zoom In/Out |
| **Weather** | 3 | Location-based weather fetch, condition mapping, preset suggestions |
| **Plugins** | 4 | Runtime bundle loading, plugin protocol, host API, plugin directory management |
| **Scripting** | 4 | JSON scripts, lifecycle hooks, property control, engine commands |
| **Networking** | 2 | Wallpaper downloader with progress, weather API integration |
| **Hotkeys** | 4 | Play/pause, next, previous, mute — all global |
| **UI** | 3 | Full menu bar app, nested submenus, preferences window |
| **Utilities** | 6 | Logger with rotation, file watcher, battery monitor, safe subscript, URL helpers, snapshot |
| **Persistence** | 2 | JSON config with 40+ settings, auto-save |
| **Particle Presets** | 5 | Starfield, Fireflies, Snow, Rain, Galaxy |
| **Generative Presets** | 3 | Flow Field, Voronoi, Julia Fractal |
| **Testing** | 8 | Config persistence, type detection, audio, playlist, display, URL extensions, math, scheduler |

**Total: 80+ distinct features** across 28 source files.
